OL,3,CNational Grid worker stabbed friend 51
OL,4,Ctimes over false theft claim
OL,6,FA National Grid employee who stabbed
OL,7,Fhis friend 51 times after accusing him
OL,8,Fof stealing his work tablet has been
OL,9,Fconvicted of his murder.
OL,11,FNicholas Ward, 38, attacked 38-year-
OL,12,Fold Tony McDermott at Ward's home in
OL,13,FEton Street, Grantham, after becoming
OL,14,Fconvinced he had taken the device and
OL,15,Fanother belong to his daughter.
OL,17,FThe violence erupted after a night of
OL,18,Fdrinking and taking drugs on 14
OL,19,FOctober last year, Lincoln Crown Court
OL,20,Fheard.
