OL,6,FA witness reported hearing Ward shout
OL,7,Fat his victim that he would lose his
OL,8,Fjob, which he had recently started, if
OL,9,Fhis work tablet was not returned.
OL,11,FPolice later found the tablets in a
OL,12,Fbag belonging to Ward.
