OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Jennifer Lovatt, of the
OL,7,FLincolnshire Police and the East
OL,8,FMidlands Special Operations Unit,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Ward's actions were completely
OL,10,Fand utterly unnecessary, and brutal.
OL,11,FWard's belief that Tony had stolen
OL,12,Ffrom him, which then prompted such
OL,13,Fanger, had no foundation whatsoever.
OL,14,F"Had he checked his own bags properly,
OL,15,Fand listened to his friend who both
OL,16,Fdenied stealing from him and pleaded
OL,17,Fwith Ward to believe him, Tony's
OL,18,Ffamily would not be without their
OL,19,Floved one today."
