OL,6,FThe court heard the attack started at
OL,7,Faround 12.40am and lasted for around
OL,8,Ftwo hours.
OL,10,FPolice were called at 4.21am about the
OL,11,Fincident and arrested Ward a short
OL,12,Ftime later walking past McDonald's
OL,13,Fwith blood on his hands and clothes.
OL,15,FHe admitted killing his friend but
OL,16,Fclaimed he had lost control because he
OL,17,Fbelieved Mr McDermott had stolen his
OL,18,Fproperty. He also claimed he had acted
OL,19,Fin self-defence.
