OL,6,FWard denied murder, but was found
OL,7,Fguilty after a two-week trial. He will
OL,8,Fbe sentenced on 2 May.JDet Ch Insp
OL,9,FLovatt added: "I would like to pay
OL,10,Ftribute to Tony's family for their
OL,11,Fstrength in getting through what was a
OL,12,Fvery difficult trial to listen to.
OL,14,F"It is finding justice for victims
OL,15,Flike Tony that we come to work for,
OL,16,Fand I hope that today his family will
OL,17,Fbe able to start looking to the future
OL,18,Fand how that may now look without him."
